00:42:52.300 --> 00:42:54.610
Aldofi [assumed spelling]
is a fashion designer

00:42:54.610 --> 00:42:59.740 position:56%
from Niger Mali now living in Silver
Spring, Maryland and in Paris.

00:42:59.740 --> 00:43:03.760
Aldofi was born in Niger and
eventually moved to Mali.

00:43:03.760 --> 00:43:08.480
He fled from Mali years ago when
the extremist threatened his life

00:43:08.480 --> 00:43:12.700
